Class Controller

java.lang.Object
Controller
Direct Known Subclasses:
GameController, GameResultsController, HomeScreenController, IndividualTournamentController, LoginScreenController, SignUpPageController, TournamentHomeController
public class Controller
extends java.lang.Object
Controller class that all the controllers for each javaFX stage inherit from. Defines methods that are override in the derived classes
See Also:
LoginScreenController, HomeScreenController, GameController, GameResultsController, SignUpPageController, TournamentHomeController, IndividualTournamentController
